ComicInfo.Title: Snake Hunt Part 3
ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: Snake Hunt Part 3: Cobra's fleet of ASPIDs ferry the kidnapped Snake Eyes out of New York with an aerial escort including a Night Raven jet; three Joe pilots engage and destroy the ASPIDs escorts while Snake Eyes tries to fight free of Cobra, but Laura 343 hits Snake Eyes with a tranquilizer.
